<html>
<head>
    <title>Grand Plaza Hotel</title>
</head>
<body>

    <h1>Grand Plaza Hotel</h1>
    <hr>
    
    <h3>Room: Standard Cozy Room</h3>
    <div>
        <p>A comfortable and efficient space perfect for solo travelers or short business trips.</p>
    </div>
    <h4>Included Amenities:</h4>
    <ul>
        <li>Free High-Speed Wi-Fi</li>
        <li>Work Desk & Ergonomic Chair</li>
        <li>Queen Size Bed</li>
    </ul>
    <p><b>Price: ₹2,500 per night</b></p>
    <hr>

    <h3>Room: Deluxe Executive Suite</h3>
    <div>
        <p>Spacious living with a touch of elegance, featuring a city view and premium furnishings.</p>
    </div>
    <h4>Included Amenities:</h4>
    <ul>
        <li>Free High-Speed Wi-Fi</li>
        <li>Complimentary Breakfast</li>
        <li>King Size Bed</li>
        <li>Mini-Bar Access</li>
    </ul>
    <p><b>Price: ₹5,000 per night</b></p>
    <hr>

    <h3>Room: Presidential Penthouse</h3>
    <div>
        <p>The pinnacle of luxury. A top-floor sanctuary with a private terrace and 24/7 butler service.</p>
    </div>
    <h4>Included Amenities:</h4>
    <ul>
        <li>All-Inclusive Dining & Drinks</li>
        <li>Private Jacuzzi & Steam Room</li>
        <li>Panoramic Ocean View</li>
        <li>Airport Limousine Transfer</li>
    </ul>
    <p><b>Price: ₹15,000 per night</b></p>

    <hr>

    <h3>Book Your Stay</h3>
    
    <form>
        <p>Select Room Type: 
            <select required>
                <option value="standard">Standard Cozy Room (₹2,500)</option>
                <option value="deluxe">Deluxe Executive Suite (₹5,000)</option>
                <option value="presidential">Presidential Penthouse (₹15,000)</option>
            </select>
        </p>
        
        <p>Check-in Date: <input type="date" required></p>
        <p>Check-out Date: <input type="date" required></p>
        
        <p>Number of Nights: 
            <input type="number" id="days" placeholder="0" min="1" required>
        </p>

        <p>Guest Name: <input type="text" placeholder="Enter Full Name" required></p>

        <h3>Total Price: ₹0</h3>

        <button type="submit">Confirm Booking</button>
    </form>

</body>
</html>
